[32m+[m[32m## How It Works[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m1. User enters a message in the Streamlit chat interface.[m
[32m+[m[32m2. Message is stored in Streamlit session state.[m
[32m+[m[32m3. Entire conversation history is sent to Groq.[m
[32m+[m[32m4. Groq generates a response using Llama 3.[m
[32m+[m[32m5. Response is displayed and added to chat history.[m
